INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2046,2,4,'BATTLE_SHIP','Battleship',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2047,2,4,'BATTLE_SHIP_DESC','Battleships usually form the basis of the fleet. Their heavy guns, high speed and large cargo tonnage make them serious rivals.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2048,2,4,'BATTLE_SHIP_FULL_DESC','Battleships usually form the basis of the fleet. Their heavy guns, high speed and large cargo tonnage make them serious rivals.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2049,2,4,'BOMBER','Bomber',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2050,2,4,'BOMBER_DESC','Bomber was designed in order to destroy the planetary protection.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2051,2,4,'BOMBER_FULL_DESC','Bomber was designed in order to destroy the planetary protection. With the laser sight, he just drops a bomb on the plasma surface of the planet and thus causing huge damage to the defensive structures. Disadvantages: relatively slow ship.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2052,2,4,'COLONY_SHIP','Colonizer',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2053,2,4,'COLONY_SHIP_DESC','With this ship you can explore uninhabited planet.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2054,2,4,'COLONY_SHIP_FULL_DESC','Colonizer is intended for the development of previously unoccupied planets. It is used in the new colony as a supplier of raw materials - it disassembled and use all useful material for the development of a new light.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2055,2,4,'COMBUSTION_ENGINE','Jet engine',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2056,2,4,'COMBUSTION_ENGINE_DESC','Technology for the development of small engines komsicheskih ships that can fly with a small consumption of fuel over long distances.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2057,2,4,'COMBUSTION_ENGINE_FULL_DESC','The engine is based on the principle of return. Matter heated to high temperatures, is thrown into the opposite direction and acceleration gives the ship. The efficiency of these motors is quite small, but they are quite reliable, cheap to produce and maintain. In addition, they occupy less space on board compared to other engines, so they are still quite often found on small ships. Since jet engines are the foundation of any space mission, should examine them as soon as possible. Further development of these engines makes the following vehicles at every level is 10% faster: <br /> <br /> small freighters (until no investigated kick motor level 5), large transports, light fighters and spy probes.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2058,2,4,'COMPUTER_TECH','Computer Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2059,2,4,'COMPUTER_TECH_DESC','With increasing power of computers can command more and more fleets. Each level of computer technology increases the maximum number of fleets to one.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2060,2,4,'COMPUTER_TECH_FULL_DESC','Computer technology is designed to increase the available computing power. As a result, the world develop more productive and efficient computer systems, computing power increases and the rate at which computational processes. With increasing power of computers can simultaneously command a growing number of fleets. Each level of development of computer technology makes it possible to command a fleet. The more distributed fleet, the more you can make raids and thereby capture more material. Naturally, this technology is useful and traders, as it allows them to simultaneously send more merchant fleets. For this reason, you should always develop computer technology throughout the game.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2061,2,4,'CONTINUE','Proceed',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2062,2,4,'CRUISER','Cruiser',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2063,2,4,'CRUISER_DESC','Cruisers almost three times more strongly protected than the heavy fighters, and the firepower they are superior heavy fighters nearly two-fold. In addition, they are very fast.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2064,2,4,'CRUISER_FULL_DESC','With the development of lasers and heavy ion cannon heavy fighters are increasingly forced out. Despite numerous improvements in firepower and not reservations could be so altered to effectively counter these defensive tools. It was therefore decided to build a new class of ships, which would combine a hotel and more firepower. So there was a cruiser. Cruisers almost three times more strongly protected than the heavy fighters and have more than twice the firepower. In addition, they are very fast. There is no better weapon against an average defense. Almost a century cruisers unlimited sway in the universe. With the advent of guns and plasma guns Gauss their reign ended. However, today they are willing to use against groups of fighters.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2065,2,4,'DEATH_STAR','Death Star',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2066,2,4,'DEATH_STAR_DESC','Death Star is equipped with a giant graviton cannon that can destroy ships and even the moon.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2067,2,4,'DEATH_STAR_FULL_DESC','The Death Star is equipped with a graviton gun, which can destroy all types of ships and even the moon. To produce enough energy, the star&#39;s death is almost entirely composed of the generators. Only a huge star of the empire have sufficient resources and personnel for the construction of this huge ship.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2068,2,4,'DEMOLISH','Destruction:',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2069,2,4,'DEMOLISH_NOW','&quot;Demolish&quot;',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2070,2,4,'ENERGY_TECH','Energy Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2071,2,4,'ENERGY_TECH_DESC','The possession of different types of energy is needed for many new technologies.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2072,2,4,'ENERGY_TECH_FULL_DESC','The possession of different types of energy is needed for many new technologies.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2073,2,4,'ESPIONAGE_SENSOR','Spy Probe',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2074,2,4,'ESPIONAGE_SENSOR_DESC','Spy probes - these are small maneuverable ships, which deliver data from a distance of fleets and planets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2075,2,4,'ESPIONAGE_SENSOR_FULL_DESC','Spy probes - these are small maneuverable ships, which deliver data from a distance of fleets and planets. Their high-power motor allows them to travel long distances for a few seconds. Once introduced into the orbit of a planet, they stay there for some time to assembling the data. At this time the enemy can detect them with relative ease and attacking. To save space not found any armor or shields, or guns, which makes the probes in the case of easy targets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2076,2,4,'EXPO_TECH','Expedition Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2077,2,4,'EXPO_TECH_DESC','Now the ships can be equipped with the research unit that provides the processing of data collected in long flights.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2078,2,4,'EXPO_TECH_FULL_DESC','Forwarding technology encompasses a variety of scanning technologies and allows you to equip the ships of various classes of the research module. It contains a database, a small mobile laboratory, and various biokletki and receptacles for the samples. For the safety of the ship in the investigation of dangerous facilities research module is equipped with an autonomous power supply and generator of energy field, which in extreme situations may surround Research Module powerful energy field.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2079,2,4,'FRIGATE','Battle cruiser',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2080,2,4,'FRIGATE_DESC','Battlecruiser specializes in intercepting enemy fleets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2081,2,4,'FRIGATE_FULL_DESC','This high-tech ship brings death attacking fleet. Its advanced laser cannons keep heavy enemy ships at a distance and can eliminate a few units by one volley. Due to its small size and incredibly powerful weapons, battle cruiser carrying capacity is very small, but at the expense of a hyperspace engine and little fuel consumption.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2082,2,4,'GAUSS_GUN','Gauss Cannon',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2083,2,4,'GAUSS_GUN_DESC','Gauss gun accelerates multi-ton charges with the gargantuan cost of energy.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2084,2,4,'GAUSS_GUN_FULL_DESC','For a long time considered to be obsolete artillery against the development of modern laser and ion technology and are constantly improving security, while new research on energy technologies are not allowed to pick up guns to a new level. In general, the principles of electromagnetic mass accelerators on Earth have been known since the 20th century. One of them - Gauss cannon. With the decision of the technical difficulties of using it as a weapon has become a reality. Multi-ton projectiles are accelerated by the magnetic field with a tremendous expenditure of energy and have the output speed that dust in the air around the projectile are burned, and the sound wave shakes the earth. Even the modern armor and shields can hardly resist the disruptive force of Gauss cannon, and often happens is that the goal of simply sweep through. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2085,2,4,'GRAVI','Gravitational technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2086,2,4,'GRAVI_DESC','Graviton - a particle that has neither mass nor charge and determines the force of gravity. By running a concentrated charge of gravitons scientists managed to create an artificial gravity field, which is able to destroy ships and even the moon. As the level of this technology can reduce fuel consumption.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2087,2,4,'GRAVI_FULL_DESC','Graviton - a particle that has neither mass nor charge and determines the force of gravity. By running a concentrated charge of gravitons scientists managed to create an artificial gravity field, which, like a black hole, draws in a lot, so you can destroy ships and even the moon. As the level of this technology can reduce fuel consumption in flight throughout the ship. To learn a new level of technology required a huge amount of energy. Column shows the percentage of production of fuel from the base value for a given level of technology.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2088,2,4,'GUN_TECH','Weapons Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2089,2,4,'GUN_TECH_DESC','Weapons Technology makes more efficient weapons systems. Each level increases the power of weapons of military units by 10% of primary power.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2090,2,4,'GUN_TECH_FULL_DESC','Weapons Technology is engaged primarily further development of available weapons systems. In this case emphasizes the fact that the available supply of energy more and more accurately direct this energy. Because of this weapon system becomes more efficient, but a weapon causes more damage. Each level of weapons technology increases the power of weapons of military units by 10%. Weapons Technology is important for the competitive parts of the content. Therefore, it should continually evolve throughout the game.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2091,2,4,'HYDROGEN_LAB','Synthesizer hydrogen',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2092,2,4,'HYDROGEN_LAB_FULL_DESC','Improving synthesizer increases its efficiency to process the ocean of the planet and, consequently, greater production of hydrogen. Hydrogen is needed as fuel for ships, almost all studies show the galaxies, as well as for sensory phalanx.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2093,2,4,'HYDROGEN_PLANT','Thermonuclear power plant',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2094,2,4,'HYDROGEN_PLANT_FULL_DESC','On fusion power plants using nuclear fusion under enormous pressure and high temperature of 2 atoms of heavy hydrogen are combined into one helium atom. In this case, the formation of helium nuclei, produced by the energy in 41.32 x 10 -13 J in the form of radiation (thus the combustion of hydrogen produces 1 g of 172 MWh of energy). The more a fusion reactor, the more difficult processes of synthesis, the reactor produces more energy. Extraction of energy can also be enhanced through the development of energy technologies.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2095,2,4,'HYDROGEN_STORAGE','Capacity for hydrogen',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2096,2,4,'HYDROGEN_STORAGE_FULL_DESC','Huge capacity for storage of produced hydrogen. They are usually found near the space port. Than they are, the more hydrogen can be stored in them. If they are filled, the production of hydrogen stops.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2097,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_ENGINE','Hyperspace Drive',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2098,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_ENGINE_DESC','Arches space around the ship. Further development of these engines makes some ships faster.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2099,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_ENGINE_FULL_DESC','Due to the space-time curvature in the immediate vicinity of the ship space shrinks faster than overcome distances. The higher developed hyperspace drive, the higher the compression space, so that with each level the speed of ships increased by 30%.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2100,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_TECH','Hyperspace Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2101,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_TECH_DESC','By intertwining the 4th and 5th dimension became possible to explore new, more economical and efficient engine. In addition, scientists discovered that a curved space increases the range of the sensor phalanx.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2102,2,4,'HYPERSPACE_TECH_FULL_DESC','By intertwining the 4th and 5th dimension became possible to explore new, more economical and efficient engine. In addition, scientists discovered that a curved space increases the range of the sensor phalanx of 10% for each level of technology.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2103,2,4,'IGN','Intergalactic Research Network',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2104,2,4,'IGN_DESC','This network enables communication of scientists working in research laboratories in different planets. Each new level allows you to connect to a network of additional laboratories.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2105,2,4,'IGN_FULL_DESC','This network enables communication of scientists working in research laboratories in different planets. Each new level allows you to connect to the network for more laboratory (first joined the laboratory of senior levels). Of all united in a network of laboratories in each study involved only those that are sufficient for conducting this research level. The rate study is the sum of the levels of the participating laboratories.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2106,2,4,'IMPULSE_ENGINE','Kick motor',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2107,2,4,'IMPULSE_ENGINE_DESC','Pulse motor based on the principle of return. Further development of these engines makes some ships faster,',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2108,2,4,'IMPULSE_ENGINE_FULL_DESC','Pulse motor based on the principle of return, and the heating of matter is carried in a nuclear reaction. It is also possible to inject an additional mass. Further development of these engines makes the following vehicles at every level to 20% faster: Bombers, cruisers, destroyers and heavy colonizers. Each level of development increases the range of interplanetary rockets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2109,2,4,'INTERCEPTOR_ROCKET','Interceptor missile',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2110,2,4,'INTERCEPTOR_ROCKET_DESC','Interceptors destroy attacking missiles interplanetary.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2111,2,4,'INTERCEPTOR_ROCKET_FULL_DESC','Interceptors destroy attacking missiles interplanetary. One interceptor missile destroyed a single interplanetary rocket.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2112,2,4,'INTERPLANETARY_ROCKET','Interplanetary missile',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2113,2,4,'INTERPLANETARY_ROCKET_DESC','Interplanetary missiles to destroy enemy defenses.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2114,2,4,'INTERPLANETARY_ROCKET_FULL_DESC','Interplanetary missile defense destroy the enemy. Destroyed interplanetary missile defenses will not be restored.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2115,2,4,'ION_GUN','Ion Cannon',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2116,2,4,'ION_GUN_DESC','Ion Cannon sends a wave at the target ions, which destabilizes the shields and damaged the electronics.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2117,2,4,'ION_GUN_FULL_DESC','In the 21st century on Earth was already in existence that is generally known as EMI. EMI indicates electromagnetic pulse, which has the ability to induce additional stresses in the circuit and thus cause massive interference that may destroy all sensitive instruments. Then EMP guns were mainly based on missiles and bombs, and in combination with nuclear weaponry. Meanwhile, EMP weapons have evolved, as they saw great potential not destroy targets, and make them unable to fight and maneuver and, thus, facilitate their capture. So far, the highest form of EMP weapons is represented by an ion gun. It sends a wave at the target ions (electrically charged particles), which destabilizes the shields and damaged the electronics only if it is not very well protected, sometimes just total destruction. Kinetic punch force can be neglected. Ionic technology is only used on cruisers as well as energy ion guns is huge, and in combat often have to destroy, not to paralyze the target. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2118,2,4,'ION_TECH','Ion Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2119,2,4,'ION_TECH_DESC','Truly a deadly beam of induced accelerated ions. After contact with any object they cause tremendous damage.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2120,2,4,'ION_TECH_FULL_DESC','Truly a deadly beam of induced accelerated ions. After contact with any object they cause tremendous damage.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2121,2,4,'LARGE_SHIELD','Large Shield Dome',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2124,2,4,'LARGE_TRANSPORTER','Large transport',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2125,2,4,'LARGE_TRANSPORTER_DESC','Further development of small transports it possible to create ships with greater capacity and, thanks to more advanced engine, capable of moving faster than small vehicles.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2126,2,4,'LARGE_TRANSPORTER_FULL_DESC','On board this ship has only a weak armament and no major technology ... For this reason, they should never be run without an escort. Due to its highly developed transport large jet engine serves as a fast interplanetary deliverer of resources, it also accompanies the fleets in the attacks on the enemy planet to capture as much as possible resources.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2127,2,4,'LASER_TECH','Laser Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2128,2,4,'LASER_TECH_DESC','Due to focus the light beam occurs, which is in contact with the object causing him injury.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2129,2,4,'LASER_TECH_FULL_DESC','Lasers (light amplification by stimulated emission of radiation) produce intense energy beam of coherent light. These devices find application in various fields, from computers to heavy optical lasers, which are free to cut armor spacecraft. Laser technology is an important element for further study of weapons technology.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2130,2,4,'LIGHT_FIGHTER','Light Fighter',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2131,2,4,'LIGHT_FIGHTER_DESC','Light Fighter - a maneuver the ship, which can be found on almost every planet. Costs are not particularly large, the main purpose - to support the battle for large ships.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2132,2,4,'LIGHT_FIGHTER_FULL_DESC','Light Fighter - a maneuver the ship, which can be found on almost every planet. He has a weak defense and weapons systems are simple and serves as the attacking vessel support. His speed combined with a large number, can provide an excellent buffer zone and protection for larger ships.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2133,2,4,'LIGHT_LASER','Light Laser',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2134,2,4,'LIGHT_LASER_DESC','With a concentrated attack target photons can be achieved much bolshih damage than with conventional ballistic weapons.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2135,2,4,'LIGHT_LASER_FULL_DESC','To compensate for the excessive advances in technology, spacecraft, scientists had to create a fortress, to deal with the larger and better armed fleets. This has led to a light laser. With a concentrated attack target photons can be achieved much more damage than with conventional ballistic weapons. To counter the stronger firepower new types of ships it is also equipped with advanced shields. However, to the cost of production remained low, the structure is not further strengthened. Light laser has the best price and quality, so it is also interesting for more advanced civilizations. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2136,2,4,'METALMINE','Mine for the extraction of metal',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2137,2,4,'METALMINE_FULL_DESC','The main supplier of raw materials for the construction of load-bearing structures of buildings and ships. Metal - the cheapest raw materials, but it needs more than anything else. For metal production requires less total energy. More than mines, so they are deeper. On most planets, the metal is at greater depths, with the help of these deeper mines can produce more metal production increases. At the same time the larger mines require more energy.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2138,2,4,'METAL_STORAGE','Metal storage',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2139,2,4,'METAL_STORAGE_FULL_DESC','Huge storage for the extracted ore. What it is, the more metal you can keep it. If it is filled, the metal mining ceases.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2140,2,4,'MOON_BASE','Lunar base',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2141,2,4,'MOON_BASE_DESC','The moon has no atmosphere, so before settling want to build a lunar base.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2142,2,4,'MOON_BASE_FULL_DESC','The moon has no atmosphere, so before settling want to build a lunar base. It provides the necessary air, gravity and heat. The higher the level of development of a lunar base, the greater the secured area of ​​the biosphere. Each level can build up a lunar base 3 of the field, up to a maximum area of ​​the whole of the moon. She is 2 (diameter luny/1000) ^ 2, where each level of the lunar base itself occupies one square.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2143,2,4,'NANO_FACTORY','Factory nanites',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2144,2,4,'NANO_FACTORY_FULL_DESC','Factory nanites is a crown of robotics. Nanites - a robot the size of a nanometer, which by combining a network able to perform extraordinary tasks. Immediately after the study, they increase productivity in nearly all areas. With each level reduces the nanites factory buildings, ships and defensive structures in half.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2145,2,4,'PLASMA_GUN','Plasma gun',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2146,2,4,'PLASMA_GUN_DESC','Laser technology was perfected, ion technology has reached the final stage.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2147,2,4,'PLASMA_GUN_FULL_DESC','Laser technology was perfected, ion technology has reached the final stage and it was thought that virtually impossible, even from a qualitative point of view of artillery systems to achieve even greater efficiency. But everything had changed, when the idea to combine both systems. Using fusion technology, laser heated material (usually hydrogen) to extremely high temperatures, reaching millions of degrees. Ion technology provides enrichment of the plasma electric charge, its stabilization and acceleration. Once the charge is sufficiently heated, ionized and is under pressure, then releasing it with the help of accelerators in the direction of the target. Luminous blue color of the plasma ball is impressive, just ask, how long they will enjoy the crew of the target, if after a few seconds armor burst into pieces, and electronics will burn ... Plasma gun is generally the most terrible weapons, and this technique has its price. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2148,2,4,'PLASMA_TECH','Plasma technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2149,2,4,'PLASMA_TECH_DESC','Further development of ion technology, which accelerates the ions are not, and the high-energy plasma. It has a devastating effect in contact with any object.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2150,2,4,'PLASMA_TECH_FULL_DESC','Further development of ion technology, which accelerates the ions are not, and the high-energy plasma. It has a devastating effect in contact with any object.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2151,2,4,'PRODUCTION_TIME','Time needed:',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2152,2,4,'RECYCLER','Recycler',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2153,2,4,'RECYCLER_DESC','With the processor of raw materials extracted from the wreckage.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2154,2,4,'RECYCLER_FULL_DESC','Space battles are taking more dimensions. Destroyed thousands of ships and the resulting debris that seemed forever lost. Normal transports could not be close to them to approach without being severely damaged small fragments. With the new opening in shield technology has become possible to effectively eliminate this problem, a new class of ship, like a great vehicle - processor. With it you can re-use seemed lost resources. Because of the new boards are small pieces no longer represented a danger. Unfortunately, these devices require space, so its cargo tonnage is limited to 20 000.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2155,2,4,'REQUIRES','Required',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2156,2,4,'RESEARCH_LAB','Research laboratory',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2157,2,4,'RESEARCH_LAB_FULL_DESC','To investigate new technologies need to work the research station. The level of the research station is a critical factor of how fast can be mastered new technologies. The higher the level of development of the research laboratory, the more can be studied by new technologies. In order to as soon as possible to complete research on one planet, it sent all the available scientists and thus leave their planet. Once the technology was studied, the scientists returned to their home planet, and carry with them knowledge of it. Since new technologies can be applied to other planets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2158,2,4,'RESEARCH_LAB_REQUIRED','Necessary to build a research laboratory.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2159,2,4,'ROBOTIC_FACTORY','Factory Robot',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2160,2,4,'ROBOTIC_FACTORY_FULL_DESC','Provides a simple labor, which can be used in the construction of a planetary infrastructure. Each level increases the speed of the factory buildings.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2161,2,4,'ROCKET_LAUNCHER','Rocket Launcher',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2162,2,4,'ROCKET_LAUNCHER_DESC','Rocket Launcher - simple and cheap means of defense.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2163,2,4,'ROCKET_LAUNCHER_FULL_DESC','Rocket Launcher - simple and cheap means of defense. Since this is a development of conventional ballistic weapons, then it does not need further upgrading. Small production costs to justify its use against smaller fleets, but over time it loses its value. Later it is used only to divert the enemy shots. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2164,2,4,'ROCKET_STATION','Missile silos',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2165,2,4,'ROCKET_STATION_DESC','Used to store the missiles.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2166,2,4,'ROCKET_STATION_FULL_DESC','Missile silos used to store rockets. Each level can be stored for five or ten interplanetary missile interceptors more. One interplanetary space launch requires two times more than the interceptor missile. Perhaps any combination of different types of missiles.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2167,2,4,'SHELL_TECH','Armor Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2168,2,4,'SHELL_TECH_DESC','Special alloys improve the armor of the spacecraft. Thus, the stability of the armor may increase with each level of 10%.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2169,2,4,'SHELL_TECH_FULL_DESC','Special alloys improve the armor of the spacecraft. Once found very resistant alloy, special rays alter the molecular structure of the spacecraft, and brings it to the state of the studied alloy. Thus, the stability of the armor may increase with each level of 10%.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2170,2,4,'SHIELD_TECH','Shielding Technology',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2171,2,4,'SHIELD_TECH_DESC','This technology makes the shields of ships and defensive structures more efficient. Each level increases the efficiency of shields for 10% of the principal power. With each level you can build a more protective domes.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2172,2,4,'SHIELD_TECH_FULL_DESC','The development of this technology allows to increase the supply of energy shields and protective screens, which in turn increases their stability and ability to absorb or reflect energy attacks. Thanks to each level studied the effectiveness of ship panels and stationary generators, energy fields increased by 10% of rated capacity. In addition, each level can be built in the defense more protective domes. Each level allows you to build a large shield dome or two small ones. Perhaps any combination of the shield domes.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2173,2,4,'SHIPYARD','Shipyard',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2174,2,4,'SHIPYARD_FULL_DESC','In the shipyard produces all kinds of ships. What it is, the faster you can build more complex and larger ships. In addition, each level increases the shipyards at 1% attack power and a 0.1 level of ballistics ships sent to attack the planet.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2175,2,4,'SHIPYARD_REQUIRED','Necessary to build a shipyard.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2176,2,4,'SILICON_LAB','Mine for the extraction of silica',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2177,2,4,'SILICON_LAB_FULL_DESC','The main supplier of raw materials for electronic construction elements and alloys. For the production of silicon takes about twice as much energy than mining the metal, so it therefore is more valuable. Silicon is required for all vehicles and buildings. Unfortunately, as necessary for construction and research, the field of silicon is usually very rare and, like most metals, occur at greater depths. Therefore, for improvement of the mine and increased production, as being developed larger and more pure silicon deposits.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2178,2,4,'SILICON_STORAGE','Silicon storage',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2179,2,4,'SILICON_STORAGE_FULL_DESC','In this vast repository of stored not yet processed silicon. The larger the store, the more silicon is placed there. If it is blank, the extraction of the resource is terminated.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2180,2,4,'SMALL_SHIELD','Small Shield Dome',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2183,2,4,'SMALL_TRANSPORTER','Small Cargo',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2184,2,4,'SMALL_TRANSPORTER_DESC','Small Cargo - a maneuver the ship, which can quickly transport the raw materials to other planets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2185,2,4,'SMALL_TRANSPORTER_FULL_DESC','Pickups are about the same size as the fighters, but they do not have powerful engines and airborne weapons for the sake of saving space. Small Cargo capacity 5000 units of raw material. Due to the low firepower small transports are often accompanied by other korablyami.Kogda kick motor was investigated before the 5th stage, a small transport increases the base rate and it is equipped with this type of engine.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2186,2,4,'SOLAR_PLANT','Solar Power',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2187,2,4,'SOLAR_PLANT_FULL_DESC','To provide energy for the mines and synthesizers need huge solar power plants. The larger stations have been built, the more the surface is covered with quartz plates that process light energy into electricity. Solar power plants are the basis of energy supply of the planet.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2188,2,4,'SOLAR_SATELLITE','Solar Satellite',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2189,2,4,'SOLAR_SATELLITE_DESC','Solar satellites - a simple platform of solar arrays, which are located in a high orbit. They collect sunlight and transfer it with a laser to a ground station.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2190,2,4,'SOLAR_SATELLITE_FULL_DESC','Solar satellites launched into orbit the planet. They collect solar energy and transfer it to the ground station. The efficiency of solar power satellites depends on solar radiation. In principle, the production of energy on orbit, more close to the sun is higher than that on planets far from the sun. Because of its price-performance solar satellites solve the energy problems of many worlds. But note: solar satellites can be destroyed in battle.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2191,2,4,'SPYWARE','Espionage',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2192,2,4,'SPYWARE_DESC','With this technology, extracted the data on other planets.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2193,2,4,'SPYWARE_FULL_DESC','Espionage is designed to study new and more efficient sensors. The higher the technology is developed, the more information a player about events in their environment. The difference in the levels of espionage against the enemy is crucial - the more studied its own spy technology, the more information contained in the intelligence and the less chance of being detected. The more probes sent, the more details about the enemy is going, but it increases the risk of being detected. Also improves the espionage location of foreign navies. It was also important level of development of their own espionage. Starting from the second level of its development in an attack on you but reports of the attack is also shown and the total number of attacking ships. On the fourth level of recognized species attacking ships, as well as their total number, while the eighth - the exact number of each type of ships. For the Raiders, this technology is very important because it provides information about whether the victim is exposed fleet and / or protection or not, so you should investigate it as soon as possible. Best of all - immediately after the study of small transports.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2194,2,4,'STAR_DESTROYER','Exterminator',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2195,2,4,'STAR_DESTROYER_DESC','Shredder - King of warships.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2196,2,4,'STAR_DESTROYER_FULL_DESC','Shredder - King of warships. His multiflangovye ion, plasma and Gaussian gun turrets can be due to its advanced direction-finding sensors to affect up to 99% of even high-speed maneuverable fighters. Because shredders are very large, their mobility is very limited, and they like to fight the battle station rather than a combat ship. The consumption of hydrogen in them as highly as their fighting power.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2197,2,4,'STAR_GATE','Intergalactic gateway',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2198,2,4,'STAR_GATE_DESC','Gates - this is a huge teleporters, which can send each other fleets of any size without time-consuming.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2199,2,4,'STAR_GATE_FULL_DESC','Gates - this is a huge teleporters, which can send each other fleets of any size without time-consuming. These teleporters do not require hydrogen, but between the two jumps should take one hour, otherwise the gate peregreyutsya. Can not also transfer resources. The whole process requires a very highly developed technology. The production shows the number of seconds it takes to recharge the gate.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2200,2,4,'STAR_SURVEILLANCE','Sensor Phalanx',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2201,2,4,'STAR_SURVEILLANCE_DESC','High-frequency sensors are fully scan the frequency spectrum of radiation incident on the phalanx.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2202,2,4,'STAR_SURVEILLANCE_FULL_DESC','High-frequency sensors are fully scan the frequency spectrum of radiation incident on the phalanx. Powerful computers combine the smallest fluctuations in energy and thus get information about the movements of ships on distant planets. To view the moon must be given energy in the form of hydrogen (5000-per-view). View a transition from the moon in the Galaxy menu and clicking on the appropriate icon in the Action menu of the planet which is in the range of the sensors.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2203,2,4,'STORAGE_CAPICITY','Capacity',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2204,2,4,'STRONG_FIGHTER','Heavy Fighter',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2205,2,4,'STRONG_FIGHTER_DESC','Further development of a light fighter, it is better protected and has greater attack power.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2206,2,4,'STRONG_FIGHTER_FULL_DESC','With further development of a light fighter, scientists have come to the point where it became clear that an ordinary engine does not have the necessary power. In order to optimally move the ship, was first used by the pulse motor. Although he raised the price, but it also opened up new opportunities. Through the use of the engine remained more energy to weapons and shields, in addition, for this type of fighters were also used valuable materials. This has led to improved structural integrity and a strong fire power, so that in battle he is a greater threat than its predecessor. Following these changes, heavy fighter is a new era of technology, shipbuilding, technology kreyserostroeniya basis.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2207,2,4,'STRONG_LASER','Heavy Laser',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2208,2,4,'STRONG_LASER_DESC','Heavy laser represents a further development of the laser light.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2209,2,4,'STRONG_LASER_FULL_DESC','Heavy laser represents a further development of the laser light. The structure has been strengthened and improved with new materials. Shell could do much more resistant. At the same time has been improved and the energy system and the target computer, so that the laser can be hard to focus much more energy on target. Defenses are disabled themselves, as soon as they are severely injured.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2210,2,4,'TERRA_FORMER','Terraformer',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2211,2,4,'TERRA_FORMER_DESC','Terraformer can convert huge areas making them suitable for building.',0);
INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (2212,2,4,'TERRA_FORMER_FULL_DESC','As the development of the planets is becoming increasingly important question of the limitations of usable space. Such traditional methods, such as building heights and depths, were inadequate. A small group of physicists and nanotehnikov found a solution - terraformer. Spending huge amounts of energy can transform terraformer vast areas and even entire continents, making them suitable for building. This structure continuously produced specific nanites that are responsible for the consistent quality of the soil.',0);
