INSERT INTO `na_phrases` VALUES (3490,2,4,'MOON_LAB_FULL_DESC','Lunar Lab (LL) - is the most perfect structure on the moon and perhaps even throughout the empire, the fruit of labor&#39;s top scientists. Each level of the M 10-fold increases of planetary research laboratory involved in the IIA. This gives the opportunity to research the most time-consuming and not reachable without the LL technology. In addition, each level allows you to use AA on the moon 10% of the power of the planetary mill nanites that allows you to build more and more grandiose buildings. But that&#39;s not all, scientists have found a way to expand through M available fields on the moon for all its greater development.',0);
